      "rationale": "Cadaveric test conditions replicate COU loading envelope: axial forces 500–2500 N spanning physiological gait cycle per ISO 14243-1, specimen preparation documented with bone mineral density measurements, fixture alignment verified via fluoroscopy. Test temperature (37°C saline bath) and boundary conditions (proximal tibial section potted in PMMA) documented and reproduced in FE boundary conditions."
