      "rationale": "Quantitative comparison performed using mean absolute percentage error (MAPE) for strain gauge predictions (6.2%) and contact pressure peak (8.4%), both within pre-specified acceptance thresholds of 15%. Bland-Altman analysis confirms no systematic bias. Spatial correlation of contact pressure distribution R=0.91 exceeds threshold R≥0.85. Statistical significance assessed via Wilcoxon signed-rank test (p>0.05 for systematic error)."
