      "rationale": "Validation QoIs (principal strains at gauge locations, contact pressure distribution) are directly mechanistically linked to the COU QoIs (peak von Mises stress, bone-implant contact pressure). Strain gauge measurements provide point-wise stress-state information; contact pressure maps capture the distributed load transfer relevant to implant loosening risk. The mapping between validation and COU QoIs is documented in the validation plan with traceability matrix."
    },
    {
