      "acceptanceCriteria": "https://uofa.net/synth/criteria/nagaraja-cou1-ortho-validation-relevance-criteria",
      "rationale": "Validation experiments used cadaveric tibiae spanning the patient population range (BMD T-score −1.0 to −2.5, n=4 specimens) with the production TKA tibial component geometry. Loading replicates ISO 14243-1 gait profile. The validation domain (cadaveric ex-vivo) differs from the COU domain (in-vivo) in the absence of muscle forces and dynamic effects; this gap is documented and bounded by sensitivity analysis showing <5% effect on peak stress predictions."
    },
