      "rationale": "Iterative solver convergence monitored via force and displacement residuals; convergence criterion set at 1×10⁻⁴ relative residual, tightened from Abaqus default. Contact pressure convergence confirmed by comparing results with direct sparse solver on representative load case — maximum deviation 0.3%. Time-step sensitivity analysis for quasi-static loading confirms step-size independence of peak stress predictions."
    },
