      "rationale": "Model use is governed by a documented simulation protocol (SOP-FEA-TKA-003 rev B) specifying mesh generation parameters, material assignment procedures, boundary condition application, and result extraction methodology. Independent peer review of model setup performed by a second senior simulation engineer prior to each production run. Checklist-based review records archived in design history file. Training records confirm analyst qualification."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
