      "rationale": "Continuum linear-elastic model for cortical bone and elastic-plastic model for cancellous bone selected based on published literature (Morgan et al. 2003, Keyak et al. 2005). Model form uncertainty assessed via comparison of isotropic vs. transversely isotropic cortical bone formulations — peak stress differs by 4.1%, within acceptable model form uncertainty band. Viscoelastic effects neglected; justified by quasi-static loading regime (strain rate <0.01/s)."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
