      "rationale": "Material properties (cortical bone modulus E=17.0±2.1 GPa, cancellous bone modulus derived from CT Hounsfield units via Carter-Hayes relationship) characterized from the material property library dataset. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification (n=10,000 samples) performed on cortical modulus, cancellous modulus density relationship coefficients, and implant-bone interface friction coefficient. 95th percentile peak stress prediction 312 MPa remains below cortical fatigue threshold of 400 MPa. All input distributions documented with literature provenance."
    },
